items.title: J.P. Morgan Asset Management Strengthens Retirement Business with Strategic Hires
items.description: J.P. Morgan Asset Management today announced that Josh Forstater and Tina Anstett have joined the firm in key leadership positions on the Retirement team. These strategic hires reflect J.P. Morgan Asset Management's dedication to providing innovative solutions and insights to support the evolving needs of retirement plan sponsors, advisors, consultants, and participants.
